385
00:18:34,908 --> 00:18:35,628
I'll go help her,

386
00:18:35,628 --> 00:18:36,828
or she'll burn herself again.

387
00:18:40,027 --> 00:18:40,908
Wash your hands.

388
00:18:40,908 --> 00:18:42,467
