389
00:18:51,227 --> 00:18:52,747
Drink some water. It's a bit hot.

390
00:18:59,507 --> 00:19:00,707
Xueying,

391
00:19:01,188 --> 00:19:02,428
here's a side dish and sweet cakes.

392
00:19:02,428 --> 00:19:03,868
