399
00:19:15,747 --> 00:19:16,348
Right?

400
00:19:16,507 --> 00:19:18,588
Exactly. Puyang Bo, well said.

401
00:19:21,068 --> 00:19:21,868
Xueying,

402
00:19:22,588 --> 00:19:23,148
