410
00:19:32,388 --> 00:19:32,828
Why do you

411
00:19:32,828 --> 00:19:34,027
have to target Xueying?

412
00:19:34,027 --> 00:19:34,467
Besides,

413
00:19:34,467 --> 00:19:35,388
