428
00:20:04,068 --> 00:20:05,108
You can target me.

429
00:20:05,227 --> 00:20:06,828
But don't involve others.

430
00:20:14,947 --> 00:20:15,908
Dongbo Xueying,

431
00:20:16,787 --> 00:20:18,068
I've been tolerating
you for a long time.

432
00:20:21,388 --> 00:20:22,947
