480
00:22:29,388 --> 00:22:30,108
Xueying.

481
00:22:31,428 --> 00:22:31,868
Xueying.

482
00:22:31,868 --> 00:22:32,908
Xueying.

483
00:22:33,267 --> 00:22:34,348
