484
00:22:35,868 --> 00:22:36,428
Xueying,

485
00:22:36,507 --> 00:22:37,987
you were punished

486
00:22:37,987 --> 00:22:38,868
because of me.

487
00:22:38,868 --> 00:22:40,027
Of course I'd come.

488
00:22:40,707 --> 00:22:41,828
