00:24:03,747 --> 00:24:04,947
Father.

513
00:24:17,668 --> 00:24:19,108
Snowflake Demon.

514
00:24:20,787 --> 00:24:21,428
Jingqiu.

515
00:24:21,828 --> 00:24:22,588
